original: Berggren, Karl Uno, landsfiskal, Falkenberg, f. 6/10/00 i Oskarshamn. G. 42 m. fil. mag. Ruth Schytt. — Landsifiskalsex. i Sthlm 25. Tjg. v. länsstyr. i Kalmar 1. 21-22, v. kriminalpolisen i Sthlm 22-23, e. landsfiskal i Katrineholms distr. 24-26, dito i Ök-nebo distr. 26-30, landsfisk. i Inlands Torpe distr. 30-41, i Arstads distr. sed. 41. Ordf. i tax:ndr sed. 32.
translated: Berggren, Karl Uno, district prosecutor, Falkenberg, born on October 6th, 1900 in Oskarshamn. Married in 1942 to Ruth Schytt, who has a Master's degree in Philosophy. - Became a district prosecutor in Stockholm in 1925. Also worked for the county government in Kalmar from 1921-1922, the criminal police in Stockholm from 1922-1923 and as a district prosecutor in Katrineholms district from 1924-1926, Ök-nebo district from 1926-1930, Inlands Torpe district from 1930-1941 and Arstads district since 1941. He has been the chairman of the tax committee since 1932.
